works.description: Kate Middleton’s wedding dress had been the fashion’s best-kept secret until the moment she stepped out of the car at Westminster Abbey on the day of her Royal wedding with Prince William. Designed by Sarah Burton of Brit label Alexander McQueen, the stunning wedding dress worn by Kate cost £250,000 (about $416,700). It seems like the perfect time to take a look at some of the world’s most expensive wedding dresses.
